name: REACTOR-COLONIAL SHIT
description: A genesis piece from REACTOR series. Based on personal art detail created and developed trough the years. 7x7 star grid contained by 8x8 static balls grid.1 frame animations - messages or just shapes. On this piece is written COLONIAL SHIT and letters are changing in a frame.Probably could count subliminal and no viewer would know that:) The piece is against the wrongs of colonialism.For example Mars could be OK,regarding people,or not:)
